- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a likely category as the paper deals with the amount of information that needs to be communicated between two parties to compute the distance metric. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as DTW is commonly used in time series analysis and machine learning applications. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possible category as the paper deals with lower bounds on the amount of communication needed to compute an approximation of the DTW distance. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possible category as the paper deals with the analysis of a specific distance metric and its properties.
